善<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08a10215e1b467ef642aac217606055cf3690aea","tid":1985980,"uid":145118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a9574b767e660495c627a724be9a9e94437fdb54","tid":1985980,"uid":51583,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"a84c5b080be06691e8ed35a04519c673fa8c6465","tid":1985980,"uid":10637,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"759ba5dbecaf28c968163e89cff13776e9a6909a","tid":1985980,"uid":51583,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T13:56:21.000Z","msg":"其實要捐既<br />\n咪開多幾個ACC交一年訂閱<br />\n效果一樣既啫"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T13:58:49.000Z","msg":"人最怕麻煩"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T14:04:21.000Z","msg":"咁就要用贊助學生PLAN啦<br />\n方便好多又益到學生"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T16:17:15.000Z","msg":"學生申請資格及方法 <br />\n<br />\n今次「蘋果日報慈善基金」（簡稱「蘋果基金」）成立「撐學生專戶」（專戶編號：S0036），繼續呼籲有心人、同路人去資助這班有家歸不得，同時有經濟困難的學生渡過難關。自1995年已成立的「蘋果基金」，為稅務局認可慈善機構，多年來一直致力幫助社會上有困難個案，現呼籲同路人、有心人去資助這班前線學生。至於欲申請此計劃希望受惠的學生，歡迎主動聯絡我們。<br />\n<br />\n學生申請資格：因反送中運動引發家庭問題，而無法繳交相關學習費用（例如學費、院校宿舍費用等）的就讀本港大專院校的大專生及大學生。「撐學生專戶」申請資格及詳細資料連結： <a href=\"http://bit.ly/2HlIx1b\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2HlIx1b&d=7FLALsszV4LuAMmN05fc6kcTp%2BQsjpNju1TtMRGBB4E%3D&h=ebdca479\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2HlIx1b</a> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />呢啲？"},{"pid":"5082a784093a6e52f9a2c908353732d4069a5bb3","tid":1985980,"uid":145118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a9574b767e660495c627a724be9a9e94437fdb54","tid":1985980,"uid":51583,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"a84c5b080be06691e8ed35a04519c673fa8c6465","tid":1985980,"uid":10637,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"759ba5dbecaf28c968163e89cff13776e9a6909a","tid":1985980,"uid":51583,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T13:56:21.000Z","msg":"其實要捐既<br />\n咪開多幾個ACC交一年訂閱<br />\n效果一樣既